"  Dough:","1 1/2 cups warm water (100° to 110°F)","1  package rapid-rise active dry yeast","1/2 teaspoon granulated sugar","4 1/2 cups all-purpose flour","3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","2 teaspoons kosher salt","  Toppings:","1/4 cup extra-virgin olive oil","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","10  medium garlic cloves, peeled","1  large red bell pepper, cut into ¼-inch strips","1/2 pound cremini mushrooms, cleaned, stemmed, and quartered","2 cups shredded smoked mozzarella cheese"